title: The Death of Gustav Stresemann
view-if: year = 1929 and month >= 9
frequency: 1000
max-visits: 1
tags: event
on-arrival: stresemann_dead = 1; lvp_relation -= 5

Gustav Stresemann, leader of the LVP, has died. He was the primary force driving the right of the party to support democracy; without him, the democratic forces in the Republic will be so much weaker.
